                                    p.fs-5.mb-4 Harness the power of user-friendly and robust knowledge base software. It is designed to help you rapidly scale your customer support and encourage team collaboration.  

                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.mt-5 Frequently Asked Question (FAQ)

                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.mt-5 01. What are the types of knowledge management? 
                                    p.fs-5.mb-4 There are three main categories of knowledge management systems that exist to facilitate the sharing and management of corporate information. Corporate information includes knowledge work systems, intelligent techniques, and enterprise-wide knowledge management systems.  

                                    h2.fw-bolder.mb-4.mt-5 02. What are the four components of knowledge management?
                                    p.fs-5.mb-4 The top four elements of knowledge management encompass people, process, content/IT, and strategy. Having individuals to lead, sponsor, and support knowledge sharing is always essential. 

